<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">昨天幫聖誕老人把禮物送來給我，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是多謝你啦！<delay40 /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我開心到不斷拿出<delay8 />
禮物來反覆端詳喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">多虧你<delay20 />把聖誕老人的禮物送來給我，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這次聖誕節成為了
我最美好的一次聖誕節，<delay20 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你昨天跟我交換禮物！<delay40 />
<tag a="110" b="3" />送我的禮物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />已經完全變成我的愛用品囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天的交換禮物真開心！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要想到<delay20 />那個禮物<delay8 />
是你絞盡腦汁努力為我選的，<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就覺得很高興呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天<delay8 />不止聖誕老人，<delay20 />
連你都送我禮物，<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />簡直是最棒的聖誕節啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我再向你道個謝吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />謝謝你！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">雖然聖誕老人的禮物讓我很開心，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我真沒想到<delay8 />你居然也為我<delay8 />
特地準備了禮物<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說真的，我差點就感動落淚啦。<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你送我的東西，<delay8 />全都是我的寶物！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會永遠<delay8 />用心珍惜的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">昨天是平安夜，<delay40 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有沒有做些<delay8 />有平安夜氣氛的活動啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然每年都有聖誕節，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是今年的聖誕節，<delay8 />就只有這麼一次，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要好好把握機會留下回憶喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">昨天島上<delay8 />大家都在交換禮物，<delay20 />
氣氛還挺熱烈的。<delay40 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你應該<delay8 />也沒有閒著吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />收禮物固然不錯，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但其實只要<delay20 />能在聖誕節時看到你，<delay8 />
我就覺得夠開心了喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>